headline: Morgan Stanley (MS) Surpasses Q3 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: Morgan Stanley (MS) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +34.62% and +10.80%, respectively, for the quarter ended September 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
